ComicInfo.Title: Part 4 of 5: Tiffany Blues
ComicInfo.Summary:
“TIFFANY BLUES,” Part Four: “WHY WOULD ANYONE CARE ABOUT ANOTHER DREAM?”
The battle between the Baron and the Toymaker escalates as armies of toys are built to do battle. But as war heats up, Tiffany, the subject of their fallout faces a nightmare of her own.
